OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781542112
OL,3,CUS singer Oliver Tree believed dead
OL,4,Cafter helicopter crash in Brazil
OL,6,F"You're a legend and will always be a
OL,7,Flegend. Still doesn't feel real.
OL,8,FGenuinely feel sick. I love you bro."
OL,10,FThe 32-year old was only weeks into
OL,11,Fhis World's First World Tour where he
OL,12,Fhad planned to play shows on all seven
OL,13,Fcontinents.
OL,15,FHe performed in Buenos Aires,
OL,16,FArgentina on June 4, and on Saturday
OL,17,Fshared a video on his Instagram
OL,18,Fplaying football in a Brazilian
OL,19,Fneighbourhood.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]
