OL,3,CUS singer Oliver Tree believed dead
OL,4,Cafter helicopter crash in Brazil
OL,6,FTree was due to play more than 70
OL,7,Fshows across 30 countries including
OL,8,Fthe UK with dates scheduled in
OL,9,FGlasgow, Manchester and London in
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FRecognisable by his signature bowl
OL,18,Fcut, Tree was known for his songs Life
OL,19,FGoes On and When I'm Down. He released
OL,20,Fhis fourth studio album, Love You
OL,21,FMadly, Hate You Badly in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
