OL,3,CUS singer Oliver Tree believed dead
OL,4,Cafter helicopter crash in Brazil
OL,6,FJackass star Steve-O, real name
OL,7,FStephen Glover, paid tribute to the
OL,8,Flate singer in a post on Instagram.
OL,10,FSharing a photograph of the two
OL,11,Ftogether, the US comedian and
OL,12,Fprankster said: "I was incredibly
OL,13,Flucky to become friends with Oliver
OL,14,FTree.
OL,16,F"He would check in on me regularly,
OL,17,Fand let me know he cared about how I
OL,18,Fwas doing. Such a great person, f***,
OL,19,FI'm going to miss him..."
