OL,3,CUS singer Oliver Tree believed dead
OL,4,Cafter helicopter crash in Brazil
OL,6,FIn 2024 he was nominated for the
OL,7,Finternational song Brit award,
OL,8,Falongside German producer Robin
OL,9,FSchulz, for their song Miss You.
OL,11,FThe track peaked at number three in
OL,12,Fthe UK singles chart.
OL,14,FIn 2020 he broke the Guinness world
OL,15,Frecord for the largest kick scooter,
OL,16,F0.16m tall and 3.13m long. According
OL,17,Fto its website the record was broken
OL,18,Fto "fulfil a lifelong dream".
