OL,3,CUS singer Oliver Tree believed dead
OL,4,Cafter helicopter crash in Brazil
OL,6,FContent creator Gaspar Prim Diaz `
OL,7,Falso known as Gaspi ` was also
OL,8,Fbelieved to have been in one of the
OL,9,Fhelicopters.
OL,11,FGaspi had more than 2.8 million
OL,12,Ffollowers on YouTube and was 23.
OL,14,FIn a tribute shared on X, Argentine
OL,15,Fstreaming channel Blender said:
OL,16,F"Thanks for your art, your magic and
OL,17,Fyour sensibility, every one of us will
OL,18,Fmiss you."
